Replying to 
@nithyavramanWe've heard a lot of talk about cleaning up campaigns in LA and getting money out of politics. An easy, obvious first step would be banning slate mailers altogether.

Until then, candidates who claim to care about reform shouldn't be paying to get on them.

I'm so grateful to everyone who came to our show at the El Rey last week, and to all the amazing comedians who performed.

The most uplifting and fun night of a campaign that has been full of both.

4 weeks left! Let's keep the fun going.
