Replying to 
@nithyavramanWe have chosen to build luxury housing instead of the housing that people so desperately need.

Timing this sweep, and several others around the city, to occur just before the Homeless Count? That’s very much a choice.

Replying to 
@nithyavramanWe have a situation at the national level where Trump has weaponized fear and hatred of immigrants to consolidate his power. In response to that, the leaders of one of the most immigrant-rich cities in America have done... nothing.

We're not even a real sanctuary city.
